
// This Hyperlambda snippet sends a signal to a session using [sockets.signal], with an argument indicating completion, and resets the [.iterations] node's value to 0 using [set-value]. The [else] slot is used to execute this block when a preceding condition is false.
else
   sockets.signal:x:@.session
      args
         finished:bool:true
   set-value:x:@.iterations
      .:int:0
